{"tid":582804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成龍：「黃大仙」來到中國票房一定不好，《紅海》給全中國人看也走出國際","createTime":"2018-03-06T13:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T02:23:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":130,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"50f79faf4f5a49ea026d1657376a088f4a3a6031","tid":582804,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chan-29_mfpOs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchan-29_mfpOs_1200x0.png&h=2876d310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國政協委員成龍今日出席在北京舉行的「文藝小組會議」，指再無中國電影和香港電影之分，道：「只有一種電影叫做中國電影了。」<br />\n<br />\n成龍今日出席在北京舉行的「文藝小組會議」，期間會見傳媒表示再無中國電影和香港電影之分，「只有一種電影叫做中國電影了」。香港製作可以叫作「香港中國電影」，或者「local 電影」。<br />\n<br />\n成龍感嘆，部分香港電影人的作品「只是拍給香港人看」，缺乏宏觀視野，故未能走向國際。他又舉例，「黃大仙」一類題材來到中國，票房一定不好，甚至可能只能在香港上映，說：「香港人也可以拍《紅海》那種給全中國人看的，你拍一些宏觀一點的、國際性的，你就會去到國際」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/兩會-稱再無中國與香港電影之分-成龍-只有一種電影叫做中國電影/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%83-%E7%A8%B1%E5%86%8D%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%86-%E6%88%90%E9%BE%8D-%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%A8%AE%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%8F%AB%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%2F&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=585191dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%83-%E7%A8%B1%E5%86%8D%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%86-%E6%88%90%E9%BE%8D-%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%A8%AE%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%8F%AB%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%2F&h=1994912b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/兩會-稱再無中國與香港電影之分-成龍-只有一種電影叫做中國電影/</a>"},{"pid":"9e402c7be63c8173906fc5577e970006c958b035","tid":582804,"uid":33875,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"無地方特色，全世界咁多電影，點解要睇你"},{"pid":"e1632296cfe3e1b6ea4c05574c42c11e4b8c6e00","tid":582804,"uid":34685,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"摩西過紅海？"},{"pid":"2d8307aa02ceb9da8f49246e9458c2babb70cc2f","tid":582804,"uid":93986,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"咁黑豹呢<br />\n美國隊長？"},{"pid":"bc3ffb7c5f3dd9bd2b7ed19e9fed7d041434e228","tid":582804,"uid":14009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:07:04.000Z","msg":"中國北京<br />\n中國成都"},{"pid":"fcab72662b3c1092c0179ab3bbab8f964a1c8fca","tid":582804,"uid":35870,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:10:27.000Z","msg":"最弊係成龍自己d片都好有港英風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如A計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5963b97e1b24a797b86b45f2893a3f1059c40f","tid":582804,"uid":21052,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"反了反了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成龍大哥萬歲 支持成龍稱帝 習總企埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df35a41172e3a4f6cb6b6ff45abaabd4f0b40e5","tid":582804,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"國際即三級 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" clas